text: Arūnas Degutis (born July 26, 1958, Kaunas) is a Lithuanian politician who was a signatory of the Act of the Re-Establishment of the State of Lithuania. ==References== == External links == *Official website Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Kaunas Category:Members of the Seimas Category:Labour Party (Lithuania) MEPs Category:MEPs for Lithuania 2004–2009
